objects.description: [Dragonfly 2.0](https://collaborate.mitre.org/attackics/index.php/Group/G0006) deleted indicators on staging and target devices by uninstalling software, removing event logs, batch scripts, screenshots, registry keys, documents, and tools they brought into the target networks.(Citation: CISA TA18-074A March 2018)

external_references.description: Cybersecurity & Infrastructure Security Agency. (2018, March 15). Alert (TA18-074A) Russian Government Cyber Activity Targeting Energy and Other Critical Infrastructure Sectors. Retrieved October 11, 2019.
